transcript:
Customer: Bolie.
Hellow.
Sir meri abhi catalog designing team se baat hui.
Mehak call kar rahi hai aapke.
Executive: Unka mere ko call aaya tha.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Unki meri baat ho gayi hai.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Hum abhi meet kar rahe hai ek aadhe ghante mein.
Customer: Unhone bola hai mere ko ke aapne jo Surekha ka number diya hai.
Mene unko bola ke aap inse baat karo material ke liye to wo lady jo hai aapki mam wo mana kar rahi hai ke material nahi dungi.
Aapki jo photos add nahi hui hai sir wo Surekha mam ne bola hai ke photos wo khud add karegi aap bas product add karo.
Hmm.
To to hamari designing team bataiye sir kya kare aap pehle bolte ho ke jo page diye hai hai nahi add ab jab wo aapse mangte hai to aap dete hi provide kar nahi rahe ho.
To kaise add hoga aap mujhe batao multi add kar diya.
Executive: Aade ghante mein hum.
Customer: Bol diya.
Executive: Aade ghante mein hum meet kar rahe hai unka phone aaya tha mere ko.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Hum sab milke baat karke khali tumhari team ko bolo ki jyada bakbak mat karo kya hota hai jo tumhara kaam hai wo karne ka chod ke ye aisa karo vaisa karo tum mat sikhao hum jo cheez diya hai udhar.
Customer: Ek systematic kaam hota hai sir agar.
Executive: Ye yahi to galti hai aapki.
Aap log samajh nahi lete.
Ek to pehli baat koi samajhta nahi aur aap log samajh bhi nahi lete.
Hamara problem kya hai ki jo product aapko diya hai wo waha pe listing hona jaruri hai ha bacha usme se aapko kya nahi hai wo udhar hum tumko batayenge isiliye ek aadha ghanta ruko hum online meet karenge.
Customer: To mam ko bol do aadhe ghante baad aake baat hogi na meeting ke liye.
Executive: Haan ho gayi hai.
Customer: To wo jo jo mange aapko wo dena padega sir warna add nahi hoga hai na.
Executive: Tumko kon bola nahi denge hum jo cheez mangta hai wo denge na hum.
Customer: Wo mere ko bol rahi hai na ke samne wale Surekha mam ne mana kiya.
Executive: Wo bolti hai wo 15 din se wahi baat 15 din se wahi baat chal rahi hai ye nahi de rahe wo nahi abhi kya nahi de rahe wo dekhta hai na main.
Customer: Chalo thik hai aap kar lo aadhe ghante mein unse meeting.
summary:
Concerns:

- Designing team facing issues with material provision.

- Surekha is not providing required material.

- Photos not added to the catalog.



Resolution:

- Executive will have a meeting in half an hour.

- Executive assured to provide required material.



Next Steps: 

None

Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Satisfied



@@@Key Topics:

- catalog designing, material, photos, meeting
